OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777395954
OL,3,CMen sentenced after woman's death at
OL,4,Cillegal event
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed after a woman
OL,7,Fsuffered serious injuries and later
OL,8,Fdied in an illegal nightclub in Hull.
OL,10,FJamie Jones-Knight died after going
OL,11,Fover the wall of a first-floor smoking
OL,12,Farea at Local Studios in Wiltham and
OL,13,Ffalling through the roof of the
OL,14,Fneighbouring business in 8 April 2022.
OL,16,FShe was seriously injured in the
OL,17,Fincident and died a few days later in
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777395954
OL,3,CMen sentenced after woman's death at
OL,4,Cillegal event
OL,6,FThe owners of the venue, Connor Joseph
OL,7,FGibbs and Connor Reece Dukes, both
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to offences under
OL,9,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,10,F1974 and Management of Health and
OL,11,FSafety at Work Regulations 1999.
OL,13,FThe pair were sentenced at Hull Crown
OL,14,FCourt, on 17 April, to 10 and 12
OL,15,Fmonths respectively.
OL,17,FAn investigation found the pair had
OL,18,Ffailed to provide several documents
OL,19,Fand licenses.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
