FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777395954
OL,3,CMen sentenced after woman's death at
OL,4,Cillegal event
OL,6,FBefore the accident, in February 2022,
OL,7,Fa licensing officer visited the venue.
OL,8,FGibbs informed him it was to be used
OL,9,Fas a recording studio and for events.
OL,11,FAt the time of the visit, Gibbs was
OL,12,Faware such events needed to be
OL,13,Flicensed, and planned to use Temporary
OL,14,FEvent Notices (TENs) as an interim
OL,15,Fmeasure.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777395954
OL,3,CMen sentenced after woman's death at
OL,4,Cillegal event
OL,6,FTwo TENs were submitted by Connor
OL,7,FGibbs, under the name of Connor Dukes,
OL,8,Ffor events scheduled before the
OL,9,Faccident. However, no TENs were
OL,10,Freceived for the event that took place
OL,11,Fon April 8 2022.
OL,13,FA CCTV camera trained on the smoking
OL,14,Farea showed only a small part of it
OL,15,Fnear the entrance, and did not extend
OL,16,Fto the external wall, where Ms Jones-
OL,17,FKnight fell.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777395954
OL,3,CMen sentenced after woman's death at
OL,4,Cillegal event
OL,6,FThe footage showed the area was not
OL,7,Fstaffed or monitored, despite being
OL,8,Fused by large numbers of those in the
OL,9,Fvenue. A further camera focussed on
OL,10,Fthe busy dancefloor also revealed an
OL,11,Fabsence of staff or security personnel.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Rachel
OL,14,FStephenson, Head of Public Protection
OL,15,Fat Hull City Council, said: "This case
OL,16,Fconcerned the tragic and preventable
OL,17,Fdeath of a young woman who had her
OL,18,Fwhole life ahead of her.
OL,26,@wD@]OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777395954
OL,3,CMen sentenced after woman's death at
OL,4,Cillegal event
OL,6,F"On the night of this incident, Dukes
OL,7,Fand Gibbs were knowingly hosting an
OL,8,Funlicensed ` and therefore illegal `
OL,9,Fevent.
OL,11,F"Any reasonable risk assessment of the
OL,12,Fpremises would have identified the
OL,13,Frisk to members of the public, but
OL,14,Fthey had failed to carry these out and
OL,15,Fso failed to put any safety measure in
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,F"Their breaches of health and safety
OL,19,Flegislation, which is there for the
OL,20,Fprotection of everyone, meant that
OL,21,FJamie Jones-Knight lost her life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
